                            <th class="p-4 border-b-2 border-slate-200 font-bold"><span class="show-en">Viscosity, \( \eta \) (Pa·s)</span><span class="show-th">ความหนืด, \( \eta \) (Pa·s)</span></th>
                        </tr>
