                        <input type="number" id="ex2_r" value="1.5" step="0.1" class="input-box bg-emerald-50" oninput="solveEx2()">
                        <span>mm</span>
                        <span class="show-en">is falling through air (viscosity</span>
                        <span class="show-th">กำลังตกลงมาในอากาศ (ความหนืดของอากาศ</span>
                        <input type="number" id="ex2_eta" value="1.8" step="0.1" class="input-box bg-emerald-50" oninput="solveEx2()">
                        <span>× 10⁻⁵ Pa·s)</span>
                        <span class="show-en">with a velocity of</span>
                        <span class="show-th">ด้วยความเร็ว</span>
                        <input type="number" id="ex2_v" value="5.0" step="0.5" class="input-box bg-emerald-50" oninput="solveEx2()">
                        <span>m/s.</span>
                        <span class="show-en">What is the viscous drag force?</span>
                        <span class="show-th">จงหาแรงหนืด (Drag force) ที่เกิดขึ้น</span>
